{"tid":1996993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真】講 係連登仔女最黃係我同凱婷","createTime":"2020-05-01T10:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T13:15:43.000Z","uid":183576,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"129461d70bc888db3a46be61b8b3d16e12b95078","tid":1996993,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>認真講 係連登仔女最黃係我同凱婷<br />\n你地要扮 我地吾會阻止 仲好歡迎tim<br />\n哈 點知你地真系吾識<br />\n黃金週個精粹係咩？<br />\n早午晚下午茶宵夜扑野都去黃店就梗係daily routine啦，我地黃嘅不論深淺日日都做<br />\n但你想成為我同凱婷咁黃嘅人，成個頭染金色？其實好簡單<br />\n入物資囉 去多兩間黃店洗錢呀！<br />\n最好學理我買齊都要準備多幾份派比人繼續買<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾撚到啦！<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家食黃店之餘記得都要幫襯唔同界別嘅黃店呀！<br />\nsis可以幫襯下撐藏獨嘅Lush同The Body Shop、黃店Factiv<br />\n巴打們買兩本古惑仔撐下港漫又得！<br />\n仲有好多好多 整手機、雜貨、衫褲都有黃店<br />\n甚至帶男女朋友去逸東開個靚房又得<br />\n五一黃金週大家一齊fing錢將黃金變成現實！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外大家去迪卡儂買下裝又好、槍街添置下衣裝都好，唔好只顧消費忘記主線！<br />\n主線支線齊頭並進，兄弟爬山 六月幫共產黨埋單！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前面致敬凱婷only，冇挑釁鬥黃成分"},{"pid":"e57b69b6baf9322a265fe06380e9b14af87db9d1","tid":1996993,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0eea06df80657a1c51c19b7b04bf53e264af0a","tid":1996993,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:33:58.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3f076470243b6da19563f9fe1b4ee08a28e897","tid":199